data.text: @srfinaa i cannot take it la. like idk la. i seriously dont feel any love from them tau. i feel like theyre just companion and not lover.
@Gorgxous_ Same here! And i thought was alone.
@Gorgxous_ Selena is going through some health issues though.
I know Justin Bieber is married to Hailey Baldwin but idk. I’m sorry... Just something is really off somewhere. They or maybe he can look happy. The next day he’s a different story.

I hope both Selena Gomez and Justin Bieber will recover from depression. I hope both will get well and feel better soon. They both deserve happiness and feeling whole. Everyone does. 

I wonder, what has Hollywood turnt them into. Its sad.

I feel like Jelena was really happy to have each other but this thing thats playing in both minds. I think that what killed them both. Despite Selena’s family... it didn’t matter because they were happy and they did find ways. Past it past. They both changed.

You’re all famous and earning millions in Hollywood yet happiness is missing. They both can’t seem to find themselves. And at the back of my head, I feel like their short ‘break’ few months back wasn’t because of them but it was something else. Like family and their mind.

Depression, anxiety and everything hits them really hard. Especially when both Selena Gomez and Justin Bieber came into the industry when they were just one young child. Throughout the years in the industry... with all the negativity they received........

6 or maybe 7 years ago when Jelena happened, they were both just kids. Don’t tell me when you’re a lot younger, you don’t do things that would hurt your partner. Everyone does stupid things. & now that they’re a lot older and mature....
